ix it. If build fails due to environment, prove it by referencing A1 BUILD_NOTES and provide exact next command.  Definition of done: - CVD 16-feature model exists. - Feature quality/source model exists. - Extractor exists and is testable. - Unit tests exist and pass. - assembleDebug passes. - FEATURE_EXTRACTOR.md written. - C_status.md written. - changed files listed. - validation logs summarized. - self-review notes included. - known risks listed. - git status shown. - no unrelated files changed. - commit changes if possible with message:   feat(android): add local CVD feature extraction  Start now. Continue autonomously until the Definition of Done is satisfied or a hard blocker remains.'
